---
// Propositie-samenvatting (bento). Testversie voor /test-propositie.
// Mini-UI-kaartjes in de stijl van Features.astro, met interactieve hovers.
// Huisstijlregel: geen em dashes.
---

<section class="prop-sec">
  <div class="blob" style="top:-9rem;left:-9rem;width:32rem;height:32rem;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(59,130,246,.16),transparent 70%)"></div>
  <div class="blob" style="bottom:-9rem;right:-8rem;width:30rem;height:30rem;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(1,162,232,.14),transparent 70%)"></div>

  <div class="inner">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal="0">Het complete ISO&#8209;platform</p>
    <h2 data-reveal="60">Alles voor jouw ISO&#8209;certificering,<br><span class="grad">op één plek.</span></h2>
    <p class="sub" data-reveal="120">Een stapsgewijze coach, kant-en-klare sjablonen en alle ISO-tools in één systeem. <b>Jij houdt de regie, Control One begeleidt je van nulmeting tot certificaat</b>, en de kennis blijft in je eigen organisatie.</p>

    <div class="bento" data-reveal="160">

      <!-- ANCHOR -->
      <a class="tile a" href="/features">
        <div><span class="kick">In de portal</span><h3>Al je dashboards en overzichten op één plek</h3></div>
        <div class="stage">
          <div class="win">
            <div class="winbar"><div class="dots"><i style="background:#ff5f57"></i><i style="background:#febc2e"></i><i style="background:#28c840"></i></div><div class="url"><span>app.control-one.nl</span></div></div>
            <div class="winbody">
              <img src="/screenshots/dashboard-full.jpg" alt="Control One portal dashboard" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="cl cl-l" style="top:20%;left:3%"><i style="background:#2563eb"></i>Coach: altijd je volgende stap<span class="cltip">De implementatiecoach houdt bij welke van de 28 stappen af is en vertelt je precies wat je nu moet doen.</span></span>
              <span class="cl cl-r" style="top:40%;right:3%"><i style="background:#f59e0b"></i>Risico's en leveranciers in beeld<span class="cltip">Je risicomatrix en leveranciersrisico's staan direct op het dashboard, met status en prioriteit.</span></span>
              <span class="cl cl-l" style="top:52%;left:3%"><i style="background:#7c3aed"></i>Corrigerende acties (CPAR's)<span class="cltip">Non-conformiteiten worden corrigerende en preventieve acties die je aantoonbaar afrondt.</span></span>
              <span class="cl cl-r" style="top:64%;right:3%"><i style="background:#0891b2"></i>Deadlines en voortgang bewaakt<span class="cltip">Interne audits, leveranciersreviews en risico's met hun status en openstaande punten.</span></span>
              <span class="cl cl-l cl-up" style="bottom:8%;left:3%"><i style="background:#059669"></i>Live voortgang naar certificering<span class="cltip">Zie realtime per norm hoe ver je bent op weg naar de certificeringsaudit.</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- TEMPLATES (hover = details) -->
      <a class="tile b" href="/templates">
        <p class="th">120+ sjablonen, 80% vooringevuld</p>
        <p class="td">Beleid, procedures en registers, kant-en-klaar per ISO-clausule.</p>
        <div class="panel"><div class="card">
          <div class="chead"><span class="ct">Templates &middot; 120+ documenten</span><span class="pill pl-green">Vooraf ingevuld</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="cicon" style="background:#eef2ff;color:var(--p600)"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.6a3.4 3.4 0 00-3.4-3.4h-1.5A1.1 1.1 0 0113.5 7.1v-1.5a3.4 3.4 0 00-3.4-3.4H8.25m2.25 0H5.6c-.6 0-1.1.5-1.1 1.1v17.3c0 .6.5 1.1 1.1 1.1h12.8c.6 0 1.1-.5 1.1-1.1V11.3a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg></span><div class="cbody"><p class="cname">ISMS Handboek</p><p class="csub">Handboek &middot; 42 pagina's</p><p class="cdetail">12 hoofdstukken, gebaseerd op ISO 27001:2022. Direct bewerkbaar in Word.</p></div><span class="pill pl-green">Goedgekeurd</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="cicon" style="background:#ecfdf5;color:var(--em)"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.6a3.4 3.4 0 00-3.4-3.4h-1.5A1.1 1.1 0 0113.5 7.1v-1.5a3.4 3.4 0 00-3.4-3.4H8.25m2.25 0H5.6c-.6 0-1.1.5-1.1 1.1v17.3c0 .6.5 1.1 1.1 1.1h12.8c.6 0 1.1-.5 1.1-1.1V11.3a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg></span><div class="cbody"><p class="cname">Informatiebeveiligingsbeleid</p><p class="csub">Beleid &middot; 8 pagina's</p><p class="cdetail">Dekt clausule 5.1. Beschikbaar in NL en EN, met versiebeheer.</p></div><span class="pill pl-green">Goedgekeurd</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="cicon" style="background:#fff7ed;color:#b45309"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.6a3.4 3.4 0 00-3.4-3.4h-1.5A1.1 1.1 0 0113.5 7.1v-1.5a3.4 3.4 0 00-3.4-3.4H8.25m2.25 0H5.6c-.6 0-1.1.5-1.1 1.1v17.3c0 .6.5 1.1 1.1 1.1h12.8c.6 0 1.1-.5 1.1-1.1V11.3a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg></span><div class="cbody"><p class="cname">Risicobeheer procedure</p><p class="csub">Procedure &middot; 9 pagina's</p><p class="cdetail">Sluit direct aan op de risicomodule, met voorbeeldrisico's.</p></div><span class="pill pl-amber">Concept</span></div>
          <div class="cfoot" style="background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d;border-top:1px solid #dcfce7">Beweeg over een document voor meer details</div>
        </div></div>
      </a>

      <!-- WAAROM CONTROL ONE (propositie) -->
      <a class="tile c" href="/features">
        <p class="th">Certificeren doe je zelf, wij begeleiden</p>
        <p class="td">Wij maken ISO-certificering zelf-doenbaar: volledige begeleiding, in gewone taal, en de kennis blijft in je eigen team.</p>
        <div class="panel"><div class="valgrid">
          <div class="valcell"><span class="vicon vb"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.44 60.44 0 00-.491 6.347A48.63 48.63 0 0112 20.9a48.63 48.63 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.9 59.9 0 0112 3.5a59.9 59.9 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.25-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.7 50.7 0 0112 13.5a50.7 50.7 0 017.74-3.34M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.68A55.38 55.38 0 0112 8.44"/></svg></span><p class="vt">Geen voorkennis nodig</p><p class="vs">De coach begeleidt je stap voor stap.</p><span class="valtip">Elke van de 28 coach-stappen legt uit wát je doet en waaróm, met voorbeelden en kant-en-klare sjablonen.</span></div>
          <div class="valcell"><span class="vicon vc"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 4.487l1.687-1.688a1.875 1.875 0 112.652 2.652L10.582 16.07a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.897 1.13L6 18l.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 011.13-1.897l8.932-8.931zm0 0L19.5 7.125M18 14v4.75A2.25 2.25 0 0115.75 21H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 18.75V8.25A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 6H10"/></svg></span><p class="vt">Al 80% vooringevuld</p><p class="vs">Jij vult alleen aan wat uniek is voor jouw organisatie.</p><span class="valtip">Sjablonen, ISMS-handboek en risicoanalyse zijn op basis van jarenlange ISO-ervaring al grotendeels ingevuld. Jij past alleen je eigen situatie aan.</span></div>
          <div class="valcell"><span class="vicon vg"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 5.25a3 3 0 013 3m3 0a6 6 0 01-7.03 5.91c-.563-.096-1.159.027-1.563.431L10.5 17.25H8.25v2.25H6v2.25H2.25v-2.818c0-.597.237-1.17.659-1.591l6.499-6.499c.404-.404.527-1 .43-1.563A6 6 0 1121.75 8.25z"/></svg></span><p class="vt">Jij houdt de regie</p><p class="vs">En de kennis blijft in je bedrijf.</p><span class="valtip">Geen consultant die na het traject met de kennis vertrekt. Je bouwt zelf een systeem dat je blijft begrijpen en onderhouden.</span></div>
          <div class="valcell"><span class="vicon va"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg></span><p class="vt">Auditklaar in 3 tot 5 maanden</p><p class="vs">Van nulmeting tot certificaat.</p><span class="valtip">Een realistische doorlooptijd voor het MKB, van de eerste nulmeting tot en met de externe certificeringsaudit.</span></div>
        </div></div>
        <p class="valfoot">Werkt voor ISO 27001, 9001, 14001 en 45001</p>
      </a>

      <!-- TOOLS / risk matrix (hover = voorbeeldrisico's) -->
      <a class="tile d" href="/risicoanalyse">
        <p class="th">Van risico tot audit: één samenhangend systeem</p>
        <div class="panel"><div class="card card-open">
          <div class="chead"><span class="ct">Risicomatrix &middot; 18 risico's</span><span class="pill pl-red">3 hoog</span></div>
          <div class="rmwrap">
            <div class="rmgrid">
              <div class="rmhead"></div><div class="rmhead">1</div><div class="rmhead">2</div><div class="rmhead">3</div><div class="rmhead">4</div><div class="rmhead">5</div>
              <div class="rmax">5</div><div class="rmcell am1"></div><div class="rmcell or hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Verhoogd risico</b>Uitval van een leverancier</span></div><div class="rmcell rd1 hot">2<span class="rtip"><b>Hoog risico</b>Datalek klantgegevens &middot; Verlies van back-ups</span></div><div class="rmcell rd2"></div><div class="rmcell rd2"></div>
              <div class="rmax">4</div><div class="rmcell g2"></div><div class="rmcell am1 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Middenrisico</b>Geen bewustwordingstraining</span></div><div class="rmcell am2 hot">3<span class="rtip"><b>Middenrisico</b>Zwakke wachtwoorden &middot; Phishing &middot; Onvolledig toegangsbeheer</span></div><div class="rmcell or hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Verhoogd risico</b>Ontbrekend incidentproces</span></div><div class="rmcell rd1 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Hoog risico</b>Uitval van een kritieke leverancier</span></div>
              <div class="rmax">3</div><div class="rmcell g1 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Laag risico</b>Verouderde documentatie</span></div><div class="rmcell g2"></div><div class="rmcell am1 hot">2<span class="rtip"><b>Middenrisico</b>Verouderde software &middot; Onvoldoende logging</span></div><div class="rmcell am2 hot">2<span class="rtip"><b>Middenrisico</b>Ongecontroleerde wijzigingen</span></div><div class="rmcell or"></div>
              <div class="rmax">2</div><div class="rmcell g1 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Laag risico</b>Late software-update</span></div><div class="rmcell g1 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Laag risico</b>Onvolledig logboek</span></div><div class="rmcell g2 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Laag risico</b>Kleine procesafwijking</span></div><div class="rmcell am1"></div><div class="rmcell am2"></div>
              <div class="rmax">1</div><div class="rmcell g1 hot">1<span class="rtip"><b>Laag risico</b>Ontbrekende back-uptest</span></div><div class="rmcell g1"></div><div class="rmcell g1"></div><div class="rmcell g2"></div><div class="rmcell am1"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="rmleg"><span><i class="g2"></i>Laag</span><span><i class="am2"></i>Midden</span><span><i class="rd2"></i>Hoog</span><span style="margin-left:auto">Kans &rarr;</span></div>
          </div>
        </div></div>
      </a>

      <!-- COACH steps (verticale tijdlijn) -->
      <a class="tile e" href="/coach">
        <p class="th">Een coach die je stap voor stap begeleidt</p>
        <div class="panel"><div class="card card-open">
          <div class="chead"><span class="ct">Implementatiecoach</span><span class="pill" style="background:var(--p600);color:#fff;font-size:.74rem;padding:.28rem .75rem">11% gereed</span></div>
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step done"><span class="snum done"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span><span class="slabel">Context van de organisatie</span><span class="steptip">Breng in kaart wat je organisatie doet en welke eisen er gelden.</span></div>
            <div class="step done"><span class="snum done"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span><span class="slabel">Scopebepaling</span><span class="steptip">Bepaal welke onderdelen onder je ISO-scope vallen.</span></div>
            <div class="step active"><span class="snum active">3</span><span class="slabel">Gap analyse uitvoeren</span><span class="sactive">Actief</span><span class="steptip">Meet waar je nu staat ten opzichte van de norm.</span></div>
            <div class="step todo"><span class="snum todo">4</span><span class="slabel">Risicobeoordeling opzetten</span><span class="steptip">Breng risico's in kaart en scoor ze op kans en impact.</span></div>
            <div class="step todo"><span class="snum todo">5</span><span class="slabel">Beleid en VvT opstellen</span><span class="steptip">Leg beleid vast en bepaal welke maatregelen van toepassing zijn.</span></div>
            <div class="step todo"><span class="snum todo">6</span><span class="slabel">Interne audit uitvoeren</span><span class="steptip">Toets zelf of alles werkt, vóór de externe audit.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="pbar"><div class="ptrack"><div class="pfill" style="width:11%"></div></div><p class="pnote">3 van 28 afgerond &middot; beweeg over een stap voor uitleg</p></div>
        </div></div>
      </a>

      <!-- CONSULTANCY (mini-kaart, 2 opties) -->
      <a class="tile f" href="/consultancy">
        <p class="th">Zelf doen, hulp binnen handbereik</p>
        <p class="td">Je implementeert zelf in de portal. Wil je toch ondersteuning, dan kies je uit twee opties.</p>
        <div class="panel"><div class="card">
          <div class="fphoto"><img src="/images/consultancy-overleg.jpg" alt="Overleg met een Control One consultant" loading="lazy" /><span class="fphoto-lbl">Onze eigen ISO-consultants</span><span class="fphoto-badge">Optioneel</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="cicon" style="background:#eef2ff;color:var(--p600)"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6l4 2M22 12a10 10 0 11-20 0 10 10 0 0120 0z"/></svg></span><div class="cbody"><p class="cname">Losse uren</p><p class="csub">Begeleiding of review op specifieke onderdelen</p></div><span class="pill pl-teal">Op uurbasis</span></div>
          <div class="crow"><span class="cicon" style="background:#ecfeff;color:var(--acc)"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7A11.96 11.96 0 013.6 6 12 12 0 003 9.75c0 5.6 3.82 10.29 9 11.62 5.18-1.33 9-6.03 9-11.62 0-1.31-.21-2.57-.6-3.75h-.15c-3.2 0-6.1-1.25-8.25-3.29z"/></svg></span><div class="cbody"><p class="cname">Volledig traject</p><p class="csub">Van gap-analyse tot certificeringsaudit</p></div><span class="pill pl-green">Vaste prijs</span></div>
          <div class="crow" style="background:#f0fdf4"><span class="cicon" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#15803d"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 11.25v8.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5 1.5H5.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5-1.5v-8.25M12 4.875A2.625 2.625 0 109.375 7.5H12m0-2.625V7.5m0-2.625A2.625 2.625 0 1114.625 7.5H12m0 0V21m-8.625-9.75h18c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125h-18c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z"/></svg></span><div class="cbody"><p class="cname">5 uur gratis consultancy</p><p class="csub">Inbegrepen bij je abonnement</p></div><span class="pill pl-green">Gratis</span></div>
          <div class="cfoot" style="background:#eff6ff;color:var(--p700);border-top:1px solid #dbeafe">Beide vormen ín je eigen Control One portal</div>
        </div></div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .prop-sec{
    --p50:#eff8ff;--p100:#dbeffe;--p200:#bfe3fe;--p300:#93d2fd;--p500:#2d8dda;
    --p600:#196bd7;--p700:#1563b8;--p800:#1237a1;--p900:#0e2470;--p950:#02095a;
    --acc:#01a2e8;--acc4:#6fd0f0;--em:#059669;
    --slate:#475569;--slate2:#64748b;--line:#e7eef6;--soft:#f4f8fd;
    background:#fff;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:6rem 1.5rem;color:var(--p950);
  }
  .prop-sec *{box-sizing:border-box}
  .blob{position:absolute;border-radius:9999px;filter:blur(130px);pointer-events:none;opacity:.5}
  .inner{position:relative;max-width:1160px;margin:0 auto}
  .eyebrow{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--p600);margin:0 0 .7rem;text-align:center}
  .prop-sec h2{font-size:2.35rem;line-height:1.1;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.02em;text-align:center;margin:0 auto;max-width:46rem;text-wrap:balance}
  .grad{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#0e2470,#196bd7 55%,#01a2e8);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
  .sub{margin:1.1rem auto 0;max-width:41rem;text-align:center;font-size:1.06rem;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(15,23,42,.72)}
  .sub b{color:var(--p950);font-weight:700}

  .bento{display:grid;gap:1rem;margin-top:3rem;grid-template-columns:repeat(12,1fr);
    grid-template-areas:"a a a a a a a b b b b b" "a a a a a a a c c c c c" "d d d d e e e e f f f f";}
  @media(max-width:880px){.bento{grid-template-columns:1fr;grid-template-areas:"a" "b" "c" "d" "e" "f"}.prop-sec h2{font-size:1.85rem}}
  .tile{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:1.15rem;padding:1.4rem;background:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:box-shadow .18s,border-color .18s}
  a.tile:hover{box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(2,9,90,.13);border-color:var(--p300)}
  a.tile.a:hover{box-shadow:0 30px 66px rgba(14,36,112,.36)}
  .th{font-size:1.02rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--p950);margin:0 0 .3rem;line-height:1.25}
  .td{font-size:.87rem;line-height:1.5;color:var(--slate);margin:0}
  .td b{color:var(--p800)}

  .panel{background:var(--soft);border:1px solid #e8f0fa;border-radius:.9rem;padding:.85rem;margin-top:.95rem;flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .card{width:100%;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--p100);border-radius:.85rem;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(2,9,90,.08)}
  .card-open{overflow:visible}
  .chead{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:.5rem;padding:.5rem .75rem;background:var(--p50);border-bottom:1px solid var(--p100);border-radius:.85rem .85rem 0 0}
  .ct{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--p700)}
  .pill{font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;border-radius:9999px;padding:.14rem .5rem;white-space:nowrap}
  .pl-green{background:#dcfce7;color:#15803d}.pl-amber{background:#fef3c7;color:#b45309}
  .pl-blue{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8}.pl-red{background:#fee2e2;color:#b91c1c}
  .pl-teal{background:#ccfbf1;color:#0f766e}
  .crow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;padding:.5rem .75rem;border-top:1px solid #f4f7fb;transition:background .15s}
  .crow:first-child{border-top:none}
  .cicon{width:1.35rem;height:1.35rem;border-radius:.4rem;flex:none;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .cicon svg{width:.85rem;height:.85rem}
  .cbody{flex:1;min-width:0}
  .cname{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:#1e293b;line-height:1.2;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
  .csub{font-size:.62rem;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;margin-top:.05rem}
  .cfoot{padding:.45rem .75rem;text-align:center;font-size:.64rem;font-weight:700}

  /* consultancy fotobanner */
  .tile.f .panel{align-items:stretch}
  .tile.f .card{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .fphoto{position:relative;flex:1;min-height:150px;overflow:hidden}
  .fphoto img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 35%;display:block}
  .fphoto::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(2,9,90,0) 35%,rgba(2,9,90,.55) 100%)}
